ign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1014785, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": 2, "EnglishDescription": "Reporting the same narration, the author of Uddat ad Daee has reported Imam Sadiq (a) as saying: In the beginning of the last third of night, you may perform the ritual ablution (wuzu) and offer the prayer you usually offer at this time. In the 2nd prostration of the 1st rakat of the starting two rakat of the prayer, you may say the following (supplicatory prayer) while you are in a state of prostration. You may pray Almighty Allah so persistently…", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Kitaab Uddat ad-Daee mein riwaayat hai keh Imam (a) ne us se farmaaya jab raat aakhri (yaani) teesra (3rd) hissa aa jaaye to uth kar wuzu karo aur Namaz-e-Shab adaa karo to 1st rakat ke 2nd sajdeh mein khoob gid-gidate huwe is dua ko padhe…", "UrduDescription": "کتاب عدۃ الداعی میں روایت ہے کہ امام ؑ نے اس سے فرمایا: جب رات کا تیسرا حصہ آجائے تو اٹھ کر وضو کرو اور نماز تہجد بجا لاؤ پھر پہلی رکعت کے دوسرے سجدے میں کہو۔ یہ دعا پڑھتے ہوئے خوب گڑ گڑاؤ۔۔۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1014786, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O Most High! O All-great! O All-beneficent! O All-merciful! O Hearer of prayers! O Donor of the good! (Please) send blessings upon Muhammad and the Household of Muhammad, give me from the good of this world and the Hereafter in a way that fits You, repel from me the evil of this world and the Hereafter in a way that fits You, and remove from me this pain, for it has enraged and saddened me.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Ay buland, ay buzurg, ay bade rahem waale, ay maher-baan ay duaawo’n ke soonne waale, ay bhalaaiya’n ataa karne waale, rehmat farma Muhammad (s.a.w.a) aur Aale Muhammad (a.s) par aur mujh ko duniya o aakherat ki bhalaayi ataa kar jaise keh Teri shaan hai, mujh se duniya o aakherat ki shar o buraayi ko dur rakh jaise Teri shaan ke laaeq hai aur meri yeh takleef dur kar de keh us ne mujhe gham-zadah bana rakha hai.", "Urdu": "اے بلند اے بزرگ اے بڑے رحم والے اے مہربان اے دعا ؤں کے سننے والے اے بھلائیاں عطا کرنے والے رحمت فرما محمدؐ و آلؑ محمدؐ پر اور مجھ کو دنیا وآخرت کی بھلائی عطا کر جیسی کہ تیری شان ہے مجھ سے دنیا و آخرت کے شراوربرائی دور رکھ جیسی تیری شان کے لائق ہے اور میری یہ تکلیف دور کر دے کہ اس نے مجھے غم زدہ بنا رکھا ہے۔", "RArabic": "YAA ALIYYO YAA A’ZEEMO YAA RAHMAANO YAA RAHEEMO YAA SAAME-A’D DA-A’WAATE YAA MO’TE-YAL KHAIRAATE SALLE A’LAA MOHAMMADIW WA AALE MOHAMMADIN WA A’TENEE MIN KHAI-RID DUNYAA WAL AAKHE-RATE MAA ANTA AH-LOHU WAS-RIF A’NNEE MIN SHARRID DUNYAA WAL AAKHE-RATE MAA ANTA AH-LOHU WA AZHIB A’NNEE HAAZAL WAJA-A’ FA INNA-HU QAD GHAAZA-NEE WA AH-ZANA-NEE.", "ArabicText1": "يَا عَلَىُّ يَا عَظِيْمُ يَا رَحْمٰنُ يَا رَحِيْمُ يَا سَامِعَ الدَّعَوَاتِ يَا مُعْطِىَ الْخَيْرَاتِ صَلِّ عَلٰى مُحَمَّدٍ وَّآلِ مُحَمَّدٍ وَاَعْطِنِىْ مِنْ خَيْرِ الدُّنْيَا وَالْآخِرَةِ مَا اَنْتَ اَهْلُهٗ وَاصْرِفْ عَنِّىْ مِنْ شَرِّ الدُّنْيَا وَالْآخِرَةِ مَا اَنْتَ اَهْلُهٗ وَاَذْهِبْ عَنِّىْ هٰذَا الْوَجَعَ فَاِنَّهٗ قَدْ غَاظَنِىْ وَاَحْزَنَنِىْ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "Ar